text: Vitória Futebol Clube is a Portuguese sports club from the city of Setúbal. Popularly known as Vitória de Setúbal (), the club was born under the original name Sport Victoria from the ashes of the small Bonfim Foot-Ball Club. ==References== Category:1910s establishments in Portugal Category:1910 establishments in Europe Category:Portuguese football clubs
title: Vitória F.C.
